51
00:04:33.812 --> 00:04:36.812
"Saori Shirakawa (21)" -Kenapa kau membatalkan audisiku?

52
00:04:36.812 --> 00:04:39.312
Tolong tenanglah, Saori.

53
00:04:39.312 --> 00:04:41.412
Aku mendengarnya dari produser.

54
00:04:41.412 --> 00:04:42.812
Bahwa kau menelepon

55
00:04:42.812 --> 00:04:45.812
